name: Self
tagline: Self reflection with the Oculus Rift
body:
### The most realistic app for the Oculus Rift

![Self Screenshot](http://brannondorsey.com/images/oculus_mask.jpg)

Using the most advanced real-time video streaming technologies, paired with the cutting-edge  ultra low-latency stereoscopic Oculus Rift head-mounted display (HMD), _Self_ has been developed with the user in mind.

### Download

_Self_ is available for free on all major platforms.
